[Student "S"]
{Partner's 2NT bid requests that you bid 3\C, so you do.

He next says 3\D.  

Partner has just described a hand with which he wants to play in game, which has at least one 4-card Major suit, and has \Ds stopped. He wants you to pick the game.

With no 4-card Major of your own, you pick 3NT.}

